[[Image:PoweruserSS.png|thumbnail|right|A power user's desktop. Note the many applications open concurrently and Qemu window in foreground.]]A '''power user''' is a user of a [[personal computer]] who can utilize advanced functions and programs which are outside the reach of normal users due to the complexity and advanced knowledge required to perform these tasks.

It should be noted that if a user is a member of the power user group, they are able to promote themselves to an [[Administrator]] with very little effort. The power user group should be used with 'trusted' users only, it is not suitable to 'contain' untrusted users.

